    Uncheck Checkbox    xpath=//input[@type='checkbox']/../../label[contains(text(),'${checkbox_label}')]//input

Zed: submit the form
    wait until element is visible    ${zed_save_button}
    # Wait Until Keyword Succeeds    3 x    3 s    Click    
